    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {className: a3; text-indent: 48px;}\n.html-preview .a4 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 301.56232686981px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган фуқаролик ишлари бўйича суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Ариза берган шахснинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ариза берган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">дан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 377.6px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic;\">(Суднинг ҳал қилув қарори ижросини кечиктириш тўғрисида)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Бераман ушбу аризани шу ҳақдаким, </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Даъво аризани қаноатлантириш тўғрисида ҳал қилув қарори қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза берилган фуқаролик ишлари бўйича суд номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> суди томонидан даъвогар </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#9}Иш бўйича даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг менга нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Даъво ариза мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ҳақидаги даъво аризаси бўйича фуқаролик иши кўриб чиқилиб, даъвогарнинг даъво талаби қаноатлантирилган.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ҳозирда менга мазкур фуқаролик иши юзасидан чиқарилган ҳал қилув қарори ижросини таъминлаш мақсадида МИБ </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Суд қарори бўйича ижро иши юритаётган МИБ бўлими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> бўлими томонидан мендан даъвогарнинг фойдасига </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Суднинг ҳал қилув қарори мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ундириш, давлат божи учун </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Давлат божи миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм ундириш <span class=\"leading\"></span>лозимлиги ҳақида огоҳлантириш хати келган.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Бугунги кунда </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Суд қарори ижросини кечиктириш учун сабаб сифатида келтирилаётган асослар</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сабабли мазкур қарорнинг ижросини таъминлаш имконим мавжуд эмас. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Юқоридагиларга асосан ва Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик процессуал кодексининг 454-моддасига асосан ҳал қилув қарори ижросини кечиктиришингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Илова: </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Илова қилинадига ҳужжатлар рўйхати</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Ариза берган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">__________</span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
